1. Use your compiler to generate assembly for each file (other than main.c).
2. Compiler you assembly using the command given below:
	  clang -m32 filename.s main.c
3. Run a.out to test your code. You can manually change the parameter that
you pass to your function in main.c to test different cases.

4. Note that max_n and sum_n call read function in a loop. So enter integer values when you run the code.
